title: Standard Aluminum Underarm Crutches
description: Lightweight aluminum underarm crutches with comfortable hand grips and underarm pads. Adjustable height from 4'8" to 6'2". Weight capacity 300 lbs.

title: Ergonomic Forearm Crutches - Pair
description: Premium ergonomic forearm crutches with shock-absorbing tips and adjustable cuff design. Perfect for long-term use and increased mobility.

title: Folding Portable Crutches
description: Compact folding crutches that fit easily in a bag or suitcase. Ideal for travel and storage. Quick-release folding mechanism.

title: Heavy-Duty Bariatric Crutches
description: Extra-strong crutches designed for bariatric patients. Reinforced frame with wider hand grips and underarm pads for maximum support and comfort.

title: Youth Adjustable Crutches
description: Specially designed crutches for children and teenagers. Fun colors available, lightweight construction, and easy height adjustment.

title: Platform Crutches with Forearm Support
description: Medical-grade platform crutches with full forearm support. Ideal for patients who cannot bear weight on their hands or wrists.

title: Smart Crutches with LED Lighting
description: Innovative crutches with built-in LED lights for nighttime visibility and safety. USB rechargeable with automatic motion sensors.

title: Ergonomic Gel Pad Replacement Set
description: Premium gel padding replacement kit for underarm and hand grip areas. Compatible with most standard crutches. Reduces pressure and discomfort.

title: All-Terrain Crutch Tips - Set of 4
description: Heavy-duty rubber tips designed for all surfaces including ice, snow, and rough terrain. Enhanced grip and stability in any condition.

title: Spring-Assisted Forearm Crutches
description: Advanced forearm crutches with spring-assisted mechanism that reduces impact and strain. Ideal for active users and long-distance mobility.

title: Waterproof Crutch Covers
description: Durable waterproof covers to protect your crutches from rain, snow, and moisture. Easy slip-on design with secure straps.

title: Designer Fashion Crutches
description: Stylish crutches with customizable skins and patterns. Express yourself while staying mobile. Multiple design options available.

title: Medical Grade Underarm Crutches
description: Hospital-quality underarm crutches with anti-microbial coating. Designed for clinical use with enhanced durability and hygiene features.

title: Arthritis-Friendly Ergonomic Crutches
description: Specially designed for users with arthritis or joint pain. Features extra-soft grips, ergonomic angles, and reduced pressure points.

title: Ultra-Compact Travel Crutches
description: Smallest folding crutches on the market. Fits in carry-on luggage. Perfect for frequent travelers who need reliable mobility support.

description: Advanced shock-absorbing tips that reduce impact by up to 40%. Extends crutch life and reduces arm fatigue. Set of 2.

description: Colorful crutches designed specifically for younger children. Features cartoon characters, adjustable height, and safety padding.

title: Professional Athlete Crutches
description: High-performance crutches used by professional athletes. Carbon fiber construction, maximum energy return, and precision engineering.

description: Soft memory foam handle covers that reduce hand fatigue and prevent blisters. Machine washable, fits most crutch handles.
